TITLE: Configuring Flutter Windows Application Build with CMake
DESCRIPTION: This CMake script sets up the build configuration for a Flutter application on Windows. It defines the executable target, specifies source files, applies build settings, adds preprocessor definitions, and configures dependencies including Flutter libraries.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rodydavis/signals.dart/blob/main/examples/auth_flow/windows/runner/CMakeLists.txt#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: CMake
CODE:
