TITLE: Defining List Prepend Function in CMake
DESCRIPTION: Creates a custom function to prepend a prefix to each element in a list, mimicking the functionality of list(TRANSFORM ... PREPEND ...) for CMake versions that don't support it.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rodydavis/signals.dart/blob/main/examples/eval_calculator/linux/flutter/CMakeLists.txt#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: CMake
CODE:
```
function(list_prepend LIST_NAME PREFIX)
    set(NEW_LIST "")
    foreach(element ${${LIST_NAME}})
        list(APPEND NEW_LIST "${PREFIX}${element}")
    endforeach(element)
    set(${LIST_NAME} "${NEW_LIST}" PARENT_SCOPE)
endfunction()
```

