TITLE: List Prepend Helper Function for CMake
DESCRIPTION: Defines a helper function that prepends a prefix to each element in a list. This serves the same purpose as list(TRANSFORM ... PREPEND ...) which isn't available in CMake 3.10.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rodydavis/signals.dart/blob/main/examples/node_based_editor/linux/flutter/CMakeLists.txt#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: cmake
CODE:
```
# Serves the same purpose as list(TRANSFORM ... PREPEND ...),
# which isn't available in 3.10.
function(list_prepend LIST_NAME PREFIX)
    set(NEW_LIST "")
    foreach(element ${${LIST_NAME}})
        list(APPEND NEW_LIST "${PREFIX}${element}")
    endforeach(element)
    set(${LIST_NAME} "${NEW_LIST}" PARENT_SCOPE)
endfunction()
```

